fields.title: War Dogs
fields.review: A really well done film that doesn't need to be flashy or intense to make its voice heard.

fields.title: Central Intelligence
fields.review: It's a nice little comedy, not too serious and easy to watch. The humour is innocent, the chemistry is fun and the action for a comedy film is surprisingly decent..

fields.title: Deadpool
fields.review: One of the greatest anti-hero - the Merc with a mouth - Wade Wilson was once a special forces operative but turned mercenary..

fields.title: Theory of Everything
fields.review: The Theory of Everything is not just a story about the science behind the beginnings of our universe, but the science of love; and how life's challenges that we face everyday, shape who we are and what we achieve

fields.title: The Wolf of Wall Street
fields.review: It's a rollercoaster ride which takes Jordan from nobody to a rich man. This movie was quite inspiring and I absolutely enjoyed Belforts character.

fields.title: Danur
fields.review: Danur memang selalu menampilkan karakter hantu yang enggak enak dipandang mata. Jadi, enggak usah heran jika hantu di Danur 3 ini menyeramkan.

fields.title: Ghostbusters : Afterlife
fields.review: Pretty much perfect in every way!  At the beginning of everything, and watching the trailers being honest I wasn't sure of what to completely think.

fields.title: Day Shift
fields.review: Vampire action action-thrillers in Hollywood are a dime a dozen, with the standard set by the golden age of Wesley Snipes’ Blade Trilogy (1998-2004) as well as Kate Beckinsale’s Underworld Pentalogy (2003-2016).

fields.title: Doctor Strange : Multiverse of madness
fields.review: Finally a marvel movie that is serious,  more violent, and a bit amount of gore for a pg-13 rating which is pretty good use for it.

fields.title: Me Time
fields.review: Art is always an object of fascination to anthropologists because it reflects the psychological, political, social, and philosophical states of the group in study.
